item.title: Everyone talks about Agentic AI
item.description: “Big data is like teenage sex: everyone talks about it, nobody really knows how to do it, everyone thinks everyone else is doing it, so everyone claims they are doing it.” - Dan Ariely This is still true with current agentic ai discussion.
